      "rationale": "Mesh refinement studies were conducted across three mesh densities (2.1M, 5.4M, and 11.8M cells). GCI for the normalized hemolysis index was computed at 3.2% on the fine mesh, meeting the < 5% criterion. We have not encountered any issues with solution divergence or anomalous gradient behaviour across the refinement sequence."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
