      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions replicate the five target flow-speed operating points within stated tolerances; blood analogue fluid properties documented.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments were conducted using a glycerol-water blood analogue at 37°C across all five operating points. No failure modes have been observed in test condition replication, and measured flow rates agreed with targets within ±2%, satisfying the acceptance criterion."
