      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) agrees with experimental measurements within 15% at all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "Predicted NIH values were compared against experimental measurements at all five flow-speed combinations. Maximum deviation observed was 11.3%. No contraindications were reported in the comparison, and the criterion of 15% agreement is satisfied across the full operating envelope."
