    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-biofluid-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is accepted for use in the CPB COU. Across all seven assessed credibility factors, no failure modes have been observed. No contraindications have been reported in any aspect of the simulation workflow, validation comparisons, or test condition replication. We have not encountered any issues that would undermine confidence in the model predictions. Accordingly, the model is deemed credible at Model Risk Level 2 and the decision outcome is Accepted.",
